{
  "texts": [
    "The results broadly validate previous findings.",
    "EE is significantly better than 1-NN DTW and PF is significantly better than EE.",
    "GRAIL performs slightly worse than expected.",
    "We have used the authors implementation foot_9 but have made some modifications to prevent the test set from being visible during the initial clustering, as it is incompatible with our experimental procedure.",
    "This would introduce bias, and may explain the discrepancy with published results alongside the different datasets and data resampling used."
  ]
}